Working on ubuntu 12.04

Remove all version of python older than 3.3 if any.

How to install python3.3:
    http://askubuntu.com/questions/244544/how-do-i-install-python-3-3 // see installation guide from Boolean guy and setup additional packages that he suggests.

How to install mongodb:
    http://docs.mongodb.org/manual/tutorial/install-mongodb-on-ubuntu/

How to install Django:
    https://docs.djangoproject.com/en/dev/topics/install/#installing-official-release
Make sure, that you have installed version 1.6.2
Also you need this tool:
http://south.readthedocs.org/en/latest/installation.html

May be usefull:
https://django-registration.readthedocs.org

Installing django-chartit:
> pip install simplejson
> cd 3rdparty/django-chartit
> python setup.py build
> python setup.py install
